<section class="block-section story">
  <span class="section-tag">📖 Story</span>
  <h2>Why this block matters</h2>
  <p class="sub">Lock the area you will redesign, and baseline it before you change anything.</p>
  <p>Today you read the area data cards for real Chennai neighbourhoods (current land-use mix, density, green-blue assets and losses, flood and heat exposure, who lives here, transit access) and lock the area you will redesign for the rest of the unit. Before you change a single allocation, you baseline its current 15-minute access, so later you can show what your redesign actually moved. Taking your own area is a real choice point, and it makes the work local and concrete.</p>
  <p class="sub" style="color: var(--muted);">Full block content lands in the Unit 6 deep build. The Area Data Cards and the exact set of neighbourhoods are open decisions (see the Unit 6 rework brief).</p>
</section>

